         <abstract id="aspace_c47e05adc71a22cbfd2b3dbb5abef3de">The records consist of correspondence and program and administrative files of the Yale Office of Public Affairs. Included are records documenting the Yale Reports and the correspondence of Walter D. Littell, director.</abstract>
