      <odd id="aspace_a669967b04028eb79e20542c7af621f2">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 4-C (YRG 4-C), Records documenting public information functions at Yale University</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_3692ad0ed4497b3fa9b8af44ab6d4ee4">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from Office of Public Affairs, 1995.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
