            <accessrestrict id="aspace_ef4cbc73d20ac1c12a6d6e1747781117">
               <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
               <p>Restricted until Jan 1, 2025</p>
            </accessrestrict>
            <scopecontent id="aspace_5eeb2c73e1bed5df37c29a1ba635dee0">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This accession contains the correspondence of Walter D. Littell, Director of the Office of Public Information. He was in charge of the corporate relations to the university, as well as, the <emph render="italic">Yale</emph>
                  <emph render="italic">Weekly Bulletin and Calendar.</emph>The correspondence, which spans the period from 1980-1989, is divided into two sections: outgoing correspondence is in chronological order and correspondence with President A. Bartlett Giamatti. The entire accession is restricted until January 1, 2024.</p>
            </scopecontent>
